data.description: Just Reduced - Well Worth the original price! Beautiful and Exceptionally Maintained Home in the desirable Liberty Hill neighborhood of Stonewall Ranch!  This home has a Perfect floorplan for a Family with 5 bedrooms, 3 full baths and 2 Large living areas. The home offers a truly open floorplan downstairs with plenty of light and large rooms, including a Family Room with a Fireplace, a Big Dining Area, and a Cook's Kitchen, complete with a Large Center Island. The Kitchen features Stainless Steel Energy-Efficient appliances, Granite countertops, and 42" Cabinets. Downstairs, you will also find a Generous Master Suite and Bathroom with a full-size walk-in shower, a recessed laundry room, a second bedroom and another full bath. The Upstairs floorplan includes a Second Huge Family Room, 3 more bedrooms, all with plenty of space, and a large third bathroom with a dual vanity. All of the bedrooms and family rooms have ceiling fans. The icing on the cake for this house is that it has a full 3-car garage that is finished with textured walls and baseboards. The home is equipped with a monitored security system that includes window and breakage sensors. The big back yard and extended patio is perfect for the kids and entertaining.  Beyond the back yard and the trees behind it is a private home on a very large lot outside the neighborhood which adds privacy to the back yard. This was an important feature for the current owners. The community has Wonderful Liberty Hill schools with an elementary school within walking distance, and the neighborhood is convenient to US183, Hwy 29 and US183A for fast access to shopping, grocery stores and hospitals! This is the perfect home for some family!!
